doc:
Maps a `Result<&T, E>` to a `Result<T, E>` by cloning the contents of the
`Ok` part.

# Examples

```
let val = 12;
let x: Result<&i32, i32> = Ok(&val);
assert_eq!(x, Ok(&12));
let cloned = x.cloned();
assert_eq!(cloned, Ok(12));
```
